12 (iii) conservation or environmental interests;
13 (iv) water-based recreationists;
14 (v) the forestry industry;
15 (vi) municipalities;
16 (vii) point source dischargers;
17 (viii) mining;
18 (ix) federal land management agencies;
19 (x) state trust land management agencies;
20 (xi) supervisors of soil and water conservation districts for counties east of the continental divide;
21 (xii) supervisors of soil and water conservation districts for counties west of the continental divide;
22 (xiii) the hydroelectric industry; and
23 (xiv) fishing-related businesses.
24 (b) If the director receives more than one nomination from a particular interest, the director shall
25 notify the respective nominators and request that they agree on one nominee.
